Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.76,0:00:18.87,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Simmer down.}Bình tĩnh.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.87,0:00:22.87,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{You and Katase-san would love to \Nrecuperate in a hot springs too, right?}Hai người cũng muốn quyến r\N nhau ở suối nước nóng mà nhỉ?
