Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.97,0:01:19.67,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{I can't deny that, but...}Không hẳn là không...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.67,0:01:22.52,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{If I take time off, too, work might be...}Nếu cả tớ cũng xin nghỉ thì...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.52,0:01:23.82,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{You should go.}Đi đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.23,0:01:25.76,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Manager!}Quản lý!
