Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.30,0:04:50.76,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,Ôm chị đi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.47,0:04:56.56,Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,Không thu hút được con nào sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.56,0:04:59.63,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{Maybe they're too similar to like her?}Có lẽ chúng tưởng đồng loại?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.63,0:05:01.36,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}{So Senpai's a cat?!}Chị ấy là mèo à?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.88,0:05:07.11,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Come to think if it, I don't think I've \Never seen her successfully pet a cat...}Ừm... mình chưa từng thấy chị ấy nựng con mèo nào.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.65,0:05:09.24,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{What do you think, Hayakawa?}Cậu thấy sao Hayakawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.24,0:05:11.24,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{You talking to meow, Shinozaki?}Cậu đang nói gì hả Shinozaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.24,0:05:12.64,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{A living cat tower?!}Tháp mèo à?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.64,0:05:15.87,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Is her body made out of catnip or something?!}Cơ thể cậu là cột cho mèo bám à?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.44,0:05:22.72,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{I heard this place had a hot springs pool...}Nghe nói có hồ tắm suối nước nóng...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.72,0:05:24.38,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{But this is pretty huge!}Nhưng nơi này to ghê.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.38,0:05:27.23,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{Pretty nice, right? \NA pool for the middle of winter!}Tuyệt không? Hồ bơi giữa đông.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.23,0:05:28.80,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{Let's swim plenty!}Bơi thôi nào!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.16,0:05:33.32,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I never imagined getting to see Senpai \Nin a swimsuit in the middle of winter.}Không ngờ lại được thấy chị ấy \Nmặc đồ bơi giữa mùa đông.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.32,0:05:35.06,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Thank you, Manager!}Cảm ơn anh, quản lý!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.88,0:05:41.07,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Senpai's swimsuit... Will it be cute?}Đồ bơi của chị ấy... thuộc loại dễ thương nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.20,0:05:45.29,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Or maybe classy?}Hay là quý phái?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.07,0:05:48.65,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Or maybe...}Cũng có thể...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.67,0:05:51.45,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{Right over here, Katase-san!}Bên này nè chị Katase!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.84,0:05:53.95,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Sorry about the wait.}Xin lỗi nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.44,0:06:03.94,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}{She went with a mature style?!}Quả nhiên là loại quyến rũ!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.42,0:06:07.42,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}{No good! At the end of the day, \Nshe's my senpai from work!}Không ổn! Chị ấy là đàn chị của mình!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.69,0:06:10.33,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Gotta stay calm! Restrain those dirty thoughts!}Phải bình tĩnh! Không động dục!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.33,0:06:13.43,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Go with a casual compliment...}Và khen thật bình thường.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.43,0:06:15.43,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{You both look wonderful.}Cả hai tuyệt lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.43,0:06:17.40,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Thank you.}Cảm ơn anh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.40,0:06:18.44,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{Thanks...}Cảm ơn...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.44,0:06:19.69,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Manager!}Quản lý!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.69,0:06:21.94,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}{That was flawless, and he made it look easy!}Anh ấy có thể nói đơn giản vậy sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.87,0:06:25.69,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}{What do I even say?!}Mình phải nói gì đây?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.50,0:06:28.46,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\an8}{You really does look nice...}Hợp với chị lắm...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.95,0:06:29.61,Sign_Basic,Sign,0,0,0,,{\pos(180,285)\fnComic Sans MS\fs20\b1\c&H000000&\3c&HFDFFFD&\shad0}{Chickening out with a safe approach}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.87,0:06:35.88,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Th-Thank you...}C-Cảm ơn em...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.37,0:06:37.87,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}{She covered up?!}Che lại?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.87,0:06:40.62,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I-I suddenly feel really self-conscious!}M-Mình đã quá bất cẩn!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.08,0:06:45.88,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I can't believe we're at the pool and I \Ndon't get to see Senpai in a bathing suit...}Mãi mới có dịp đến hồ bơi mà chị ấy lại giấu...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.40,0:06:48.87,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Maybe I should just ask her to show it to me?}Hay là mình chỉ cần nói thẳng ra?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.35,0:06:51.89,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}{No, that'd be sexual harassment.}Không, thế thì khác nào quấy rối.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.48,0:06:58.36,Main,Hayakwa,0,0,0,,{Come to think of it, \Nwhat's with the inner tube?}Cơ mà cái phao này là sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.36,0:07:00.41,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{I bought it just now.}Tôi vừa mua nó đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.41,0:07:01.48,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{You work fast.}Nhanh quá nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.92,0:07:06.65,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{Okay, Manager, let's head \Nto the river pool with that inner tube.}Vậy thì đến chỗ hồ kia chơi thôi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.65,0:07:08.00,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{Sounds good!}Nghe hay đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.30,0:07:08.81,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{The river pool...?}Hồ...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.00,0:07:08.81,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{\an8}{Come on, then!}Đi thôi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.81,0:07:09.53,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{Sure!}Ừm!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.53,0:07:13.63,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}{That's right! If we get in the pool, \NI'll naturally get to see the swimsuit!}Phải rồi! Nếu xuống hồ bơi thì phải cởi áo khoác!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.03,0:07:15.20,Main,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fntimes new roman\fs20\b1\c&H000000&\3c&HFDFFFD&\shad0\pos(320,300)}{IQ reduced to 3 by impure thoughts}IQ trừ 3 điểm
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.63,0:07:15.20,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}{Good job, Hayakawa!}Hay lắm Hayakawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.20,0:07:17.20,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Senpai, come on!}Đi thôi nào!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.20,0:07:19.70,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{You all can go on and have fun.}Em có thể đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.52,0:07:24.09,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}{She must really not want me to look at her...}Chị ấy không muốn bị nhìn đến thế sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.21,0:07:27.59,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{\i1}{The problem is that I can't swim!}Mình có biết bơi đâu?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.59,0:07:30.14,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Th-Then maybe the wave pool...}V-Vậy hồ tạo sóng?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.14,0:07:31.93,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{You all can go on ahead.}Em có thể đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.93,0:07:33.26,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{The kiddie pool...?}Hồ cho trẻ em...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.26,0:07:34.34,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Go on.}Đi đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.85,0:07:45.46,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Senpai, can you not swim?}Chị không biết bơi ạ?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.98,0:07:52.54,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{It's not that I can't. \NIt's just that I never have before!}Không phải là không biết mà là chưa từng bơi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.54,0:07:54.99,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{That would mean that you can't, wouldn't it?}Tức là không biết phải không?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.72,0:08:02.50,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{S-Sorry! I shouldn't make fun.}Xin lỗi! Em không cố ý!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.17,0:08:05.05,Main,Kid,0,0,0,,{I want ice cream!}Con muốn ăn kem!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.05,0:08:07.63,Main,Mother,0,0,0,,{\an8}{Let's go ask dad, then.}Để mẹ hỏi ba.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.22,0:08:09.48,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{When I was little... \NI went into the deep end of the pool,}Hồi còn nhỏ... chị bị chìm ở hồ bơi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.48,0:08:12.09,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{lost my footing, and almost drowned...}chân không chạm đáy và gần như bất tỉnh...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.12,0:08:15.48,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{I've had trouble with it ever since.}Từ đó trở đi...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.89,0:08:19.39,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{\an8}{Round and around and around—}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.32,0:08:19.39,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{I do think that it looks like fun, but...}Chị cũng biết là nó sẽ rất vui...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.43,0:08:19.39,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{\an8}{Manager, slow down!}Anh quay từ từ thôi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.16,0:08:24.86,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{In that case, do you want to go in together?}Vậy chị có muốn xuống cùng em không?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.63,0:08:29.15,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{I'm tall enough that I can stand on the bottom,}Em đủ cao để đứng dưới nước,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.15,0:08:31.21,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{and we can watch out for each other.}và chúng ta có thể quan sát nhau.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.18,0:08:39.22,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{I'll give it a try.}Chị sẽ thử.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.32,0:08:45.12,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{This is warmer than I imagined.}Ấm hơn chị nghĩ.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.45,0:08:47.37,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Are you scared?}Chị có sợ không?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.37,0:08:48.13,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Not at all!}Không.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.90,0:08:52.13,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{I almost feel like I could \Nstart swimming already!}Cảm giác chị có thể nổi được.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.88,0:08:59.03,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{What's wrong, Shinozaki-san?!}Sao thế Shinozaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.03,0:08:59.98,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Nothing.}Không ạ.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.98,0:09:04.02,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}{She's trying so hard! \NCast out those wicked thoughts, me!}Chị ấy đang cố hết sức! Mình không được cửng!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.02,0:09:05.05,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Well...}Vậy thì...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.88,0:09:08.51,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Could you teach me how to swim now?}Em có thể dạy chị bơi không?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.51,0:09:10.27,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Is this gonna work?}Ổn không đây...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.09,0:09:14.15,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{For starters, \Ntry putting your face into the water.}Đầu tiên hãy hít thở dưới nước.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.15,0:09:18.76,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Got it! Watch me! Here I go!}Đã hiểu! Xem chị đây!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.69,0:09:22.91,Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{She might actually figure this out quickly—}Chị ấy học nhanh thế này thì--
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.13,0:09:26.42,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Or not!}Hoặc không.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.75,0:09:31.47,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{I can normally put my face underwater \Nwith no problem... What's going on?}Bình thường chị vẫn\N úp mặt xuống nước khi tắm mà...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.47,0:09:34.05,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{You're probably nervous \Nbecause of the location.}Có vẻ là lo lắng vì môi trường khác biệt.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.52,0:09:36.93,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Maybe if you imagine \Nyou're in the bath, it'll be easier.}Hay chị thử tưởng tượng đang ở nhà mình xem.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.93,0:09:41.26,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{\i1}{The bath, the bath, the bath...}Bồn tắm bồn tắm...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.33,0:09:45.85,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}{She's acting like a cat that hates bathing!}Sao như kiểu mèo ghét tắm vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.25,0:09:48.81,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Maybe submerging your face \Nis a little too much to start with.}Có lẽ mới vào tập úp mặt xuống nước hơi khó...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.81,0:09:50.25,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Sorry...}Xin lỗi em...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.25,0:09:54.48,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{It's okay. Let's start with an inner tube \Nand have you practice swimming.}Không sao. Bắt đầu với phao bơi trước vậy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.48,0:09:55.86,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{I'll go buy one.}Em sẽ mua 1 cái.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.68,0:10:00.99,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Shinozaki-san?}Shinozaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.36,0:10:03.74,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Not good! I've got a cramp.}Chết! Chuột rút!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.74,0:10:06.60,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I got careless because the water's so shallow!}Mình bất cẩn vì tưởng nước nông!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.60,0:10:08.75,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Someone... help...}Ai đó... cứu...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.37,0:10:16.76,Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{S-Senpai?}Chị?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.62,0:10:19.68,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Senpa—}Chị--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.68,0:10:22.18,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Live!}Sống lại đi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.63,0:10:25.18,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{I-I'm okay! I'm alive!}Em ổn mà!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.50,0:10:26.62,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{How are you feeling?}Em thấy sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.62,0:10:28.10,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{All good.}Không sao ạ.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.87,0:10:34.44,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Thank goodness...}May quá...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.14,0:10:41.74,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{I thought you might die.}Chị tưởng em chết đó...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.20,0:10:47.20,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{No, it's okay! I'm feeling great!}Không không! Em vẫn khoẻ mà!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.20,0:10:50.08,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Don't worry! You can relax!}Đừng lo! Chị cứ an tâm!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.08,0:10:51.28,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Okay.}Ừm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.28,0:10:52.90,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{More importantly, Senpai...}Quan trọng hơn là...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.22,0:10:55.96,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{You just swam.}Chị vừa bơi đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.47,0:11:02.41,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Oh, come on! That's not more important!}Thôi nào! Vấn đề không phải chỗ đó!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.59,0:11:02.97,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\an8}{S-Sorry...}X-Xin lỗi...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.62,0:11:05.68,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Huh... dizzy...}Ủa? Đau đầu quá...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.68,0:11:07.47,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Had I not caught my breath yet?...}Thiếu oxi hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.60,0:11:10.73,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I-I can't fall...}Không đứng được...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.20,0:11:21.07,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Th...}Ch...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.07,0:11:23.82,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}{This is bad!}Chết cha!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.28,0:11:26.16,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Safe!}An toàn!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.17,0:11:36.67,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{L-Let me retie that for you.}Để em cột lại...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.61,0:11:41.93,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Yeah...}Ừm...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.57,0:11:44.89,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}{There.}Xong.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.89,0:11:45.85,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{\an8}{Sneak...}Dòm...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.89,0:11:46.93,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Nobody saw that, right?}Không ai thấy cả nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.72,0:11:48.78,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Um...}À...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.18,0:11:52.44,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{I'm so sorry! I don't know \Nhow to make it up to you!}Em xin lỗi! Em không biết phải giải thích sao...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.32,0:11:56.28,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Is that all you have to say?}Em chỉ muốn nói thế thôi à?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.26,0:12:00.19,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{D-Do you want me to bow?! \NOr maybe a written apology?!}C-Chị muốn em quỳ xin lỗi ạ?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.24,0:12:03.30,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Never mind, then.}Bỏ đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.20,0:12:05.00,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Sulk...}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.00,0:12:06.70,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{S-Senpai?!}C-Chị ơi?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.89,0:12:21.14,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{\i1}{My Tiny Senpai}{\i0}{.}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.57,0:12:26.44,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{I took a dip in the baths already.}Chị đã vào tắm trước rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.97,0:12:34.98,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{Oooh, that hits the spot...}Chà... phê quá...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.61,0:12:39.98,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{I can feel the exhaustion washing away.}Cảm giác mệt mỏi được gột sạch luôn.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.50,0:12:43.84,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{Christmas, the end of the year, \Nand then New Year's...}Giáng sinh, cuối năm, năm mới...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.84,0:12:46.89,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{I think Japan might cram too many \Nevents into such small a window.}Nhật Bản nhồi nhét nhiều ngày lễ vào quá nhỉ...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.68,0:12:48.99,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Maybe.}Ừm...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.52,0:12:52.75,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{But I do feel really refreshed after today.}Nhưng hôm nay chị đã rất thoải mái đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.75,0:12:56.46,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Thank you for inviting me, Hayakawa-san.}Cảm ơn vì đã mời chị nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.46,0:12:58.50,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{No, thanks for coming.}Không không, cảm ơn vì chị đã đến.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.50,0:13:00.35,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{If it was just me,}Nếu chỉ có mình em,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.35,0:13:04.82,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{I would've probably just whined about wanting \Nto go and never actually done anything.}em sẽ chỉ nói mồm mà không bao giờ thực hiện.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.49,0:13:10.01,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{And I definitely wouldn't have done \Nanything as active as playing in the pool.}Và em sẽ chẳng bao giờ vui đùa ở hồ bơi đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.12,0:13:18.02,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{I guess so. It's been a long time since \NI've worn a swimsuit, too. It was fun.}Phải nhỉ. Cũng lâu rồi chị mới đi bơi, vui thật đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.59,0:13:21.53,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{It was fun, but...}Vui nhưng mà...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.07,0:13:25.78,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{I feel like I've embarrassed myself a bit, too.}Cảm giác hơi xấu hổ...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.78,0:13:29.82,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{I need to regain my honor \Nas a senpai before bedtime!}Phải gỡ lại danh dự của một đàn chị thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.71,0:13:34.29,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Shinozaki-san!}Shinozaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.46,0:13:38.16,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Say "ahhh."}Aaa nào.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.16,0:13:40.54,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Wh-Wh-Whoa, Senpai!}K-Khoan đã!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.54,0:13:43.99,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Okay, who gave Senpai booze?!}Ai cho chị ấy uống rượu thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.54,0:13:46.05,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{\an8}{Come on, come on, "ahhh!"}Nào nào aaa đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.50,0:13:46.05,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{No one at all.}Không một ai.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.55,0:13:48.09,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{No one stopped her, either, though.}Không một ai ngăn cản.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.09,0:13:49.56,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Maybe you should have?!}Cản lại đi ạ!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.56,0:13:52.18,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Don't you remember \Nwhat happened with the chocolates before?!}Anh không nhớ vụ lần trước à?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.18,0:13:53.31,Flashback,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Hayakawa-shan!}Hayakawa-shan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.31,0:13:54.56,Flashback,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Smooch!}Chụt.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.89,0:13:57.19,Flashback,Shiori,0,0,0,,{I am so, so grateful!}Cảm ơn rất nhiều!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.19,0:14:01.34,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{I guess that was a thing! Must've forgot.}Có chuyện đó à? Tôi quên rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.34,0:14:03.05,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{I seriously doubt you forgot.}Anh mà quên á?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.23,0:14:07.15,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Oh, man, my drink...}A, rượu của mình...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.15,0:14:08.91,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Oh, dear!}Chết...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.91,0:14:10.78,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Let me wipe that up.}Để chị lau cho.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.08,0:14:13.91,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{I-It's okay! I can handle it!}Không sao, em tự lau!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.91,0:14:15.83,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{No...}Không...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.83,0:14:19.42,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Today, until bed...}Hôm nay trước khi ngủ...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.42,0:14:22.34,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Senpai is gonna take care of everything.}Chị sẽ chăm sóc em thật chu đáo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.20,0:14:26.84,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{No, it's s-s-seriously fine!}Không, e-e-em ổn mà!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.46,0:14:29.77,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,Em đau bụng hả?{Do you have an upset tummy?}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.77,0:14:32.21,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{I can rub it for you.}Chị xoa bụng cho.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.21,0:14:33.34,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{That's okay!}Không sao ạ.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.34,0:14:37.00,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Don't be shy now, come on...}Đừng xấu hổ mà, thôi nào...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.00,0:14:39.48,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{What's going on?! \NWhat kind of drunken behavior is this?!}Gì thế này? Lần này là sao vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.48,0:14:40.70,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{\an8}{Does your tummy hurt?}Bụng em có đau không?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.70,0:14:41.98,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\an8}{I'm telling you, it's fine!}Em không sao!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.87,0:14:44.59,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{Does Katase-san get \Nmore intense when she's drunk?}Chị ấy... cởi mở hơn khi say nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.98,0:14:46.48,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\an8}{Please stop! You can't! This is... too much!}Dừng lại đi! Chị mà làm nữa em sẽ...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.59,0:14:46.03,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{Seems like it.}Có vẻ thế.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.03,0:14:47.57,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{Earlier, in the bath...}Lúc nãy trong bồn tắm...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.48,0:14:47.57,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\an8}{I'm really fine!}Em rất ổn!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.57,0:14:51.54,Flashback,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{I need to regain my honor \Nas a senpai before bedtime!}Phải gỡ gạc lại trước khi đi ngủ.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.37,0:14:54.81,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{After what she said...}Sau những gì đã nói...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.81,0:14:55.87,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{Maybe that's why.}Có thể đó là lý do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.87,0:14:59.33,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{I don't see what she has to \Nmake up for in the first place.}Có gì đâu mà phải gỡ gạc.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.87,0:15:01.37,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{\an8}{Turn this way!}Quay lại đây đi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.33,0:15:01.37,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{She probably just wants to show off a little,}Chị ấy chỉ muốn thể hiện chút thôi mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.86,0:15:03.50,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{as your senpai.}Với tư cách đàn chị của cậu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.91,0:15:10.38,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Okay, Shinozaki-san, let's wipe that mouth!}Shinozaki, để chị lau miệng nhé!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.38,0:15:12.96,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I have to admit, this situation...}Cơ mà tình huống này...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.96,0:15:15.72,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}{It's nice, but it's so awkward!}Vừa sướng vừa mệt.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.64,0:15:18.27,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Hayakawa! Help!}Hayakawa! Giúp!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.27,0:15:20.02,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{Sorry, Shinozaki.}Xin lỗi Shinozaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.44,0:15:24.32,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{I'm feeling like another dip in \Nthe open air bath, since we're here.}Tớ sẽ đi tắm ở bồn lộ thiên.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.32,0:15:25.65,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{Oh, me, too.}Tôi cũng đi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.16,0:15:28.85,Main,Both,0,0,0,,{See ya!}Gặp sau nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.85,0:15:30.65,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Traitors!}Phản bội!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.78,0:15:34.86,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Shinozaki-san, say "ahhh" again...}Shinozaki, aaa đi nào.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.86,0:15:37.16,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I'm alone with Senpai \Nwhen she's acting like this?!}Mình ở riêng với chị ấy trong tình trạng này?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.16,0:15:39.66,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}{In that case...}Nếu thế thì...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.66,0:15:44.01,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I'll play along to the end \Nso she can go to bed satisfied!}Mình sẽ chơi cùng đến khi chị ấy thoả mãn.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.68,0:15:46.86,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Tastes good?}Ngon không?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.86,0:15:48.42,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Tastes good...}Ngon lắm...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.17,0:15:52.18,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{After dinner comes brushing teeth!}Sau bữa ăn là đến giờ chải răng...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.63,0:15:56.58,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{I can't brush them like this.}Em không thể chải chúng như thế.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.80,0:15:59.40,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Right over here.}Nằm xuống đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.40,0:16:01.43,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{O-O-On your lap?!}T-Trên đùi chị á?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.43,0:16:04.32,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Does it hurt anywhere?}Có đau không?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.32,0:16:05.60,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Nope.}Không ạ...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.60,0:16:08.19,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Come forth, all of my restraint!}Đừng có cửng lên nhé!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.19,0:16:11.98,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Once we're done, you'll go \Ngoosh goosh with your mouth.}Khi nào xong, em sẽ xúc miệng nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.98,0:16:14.70,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}{That onomatopoeia sounds kind of dirty!}Nghe dâm dục quá vậy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.86,0:16:18.70,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{What a nice brushing! Clap clap clap!}Em đã chải răng tốt lắm, vỗ tay nào!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.16,0:16:22.80,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}{As nice as this is... I can't take much more...}Mình cũng khá vui nhưng\N thằng em không chịu nổi rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.80,0:16:24.64,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{At this point, I just want to go to bed.}Mình muốn đi ngủ ngay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.64,0:16:26.88,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Are you sweepy, Shinozaki-san?}Em buồn ngủ hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.88,0:16:28.46,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Uh, well...}À vâng...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.86,0:16:30.46,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{In that case...}Thế thì...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.93,0:16:33.97,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Senpai will put you to bed.}Chị sẽ dỗ em ngủ.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.23,0:16:43.98,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{I-I can't sleep yet!}E-Em chưa muốn ngủ!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.98,0:16:46.81,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{That's no good. No staying up late!}Không được. Không thức khuya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.90,0:16:52.49,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Isn't it time for good boys to go to sleep?}Bé ngoan phải ngủ sớm.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.49,0:16:54.86,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}{There is no chance I'm sleeping!}Thế này sao ngủ được hả trời?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.62,0:17:00.28,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{Huh, that's weird.}Lạ quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.28,0:17:02.91,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{I was sure I brought it with me...}Em nhớ là có mang theo rồi...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.91,0:17:04.12,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{She forgot something?!}Quên gì sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.69,0:17:05.75,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Oh, crap...}Chết...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.08,0:17:09.75,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}{If they show up now, \Nit's gonna be really annoying!}Nếu họ thấy cảnh này... sẽ phiền phức lắm!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.75,0:17:11.83,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{We'll celebrate with red bean breakfast!}Phải ăn sáng bằng đậu đỏ!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.71,0:17:14.32,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{Hello, Onee-san?}Chị gái hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.32,0:17:16.01,Main,Yutaka,0,0,0,,{What?! They're getting married?}Sao? Cưới rồi chưa?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.01,0:17:18.26,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I need to avoid that at all costs!}Phải né cái đó bằng mọi giá!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.68,0:17:20.12,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,Shinozaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.12,0:17:22.60,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{Weird, the lights are off.}Ủa? Đèn tắt rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.72,0:17:27.10,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{And they're both gone...}Cơ mà họ đi đâu rồi?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.55,0:17:29.37,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{I wonder if they went out.}Đi ra ngoài à?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.37,0:17:31.80,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{We didn't run into them in the halls, either.}Có thấy ai đi ra sảnh đâu nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.80,0:17:34.20,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I hid without thinking!}Mình đã trốn mà không kịp nghĩ.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.20,0:17:36.61,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}{But if she forgot something, \Nthey'll probably leave soon...}Họ quên gì đó thì sẽ đi sớm thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.61,0:17:38.22,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{Find it?}Thấy chưa em?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.22,0:17:39.62,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,Lạ ghê...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.21,0:17:42.70,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{I thought I put it in here.}Em tưởng bỏ trong này...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.70,0:17:47.12,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{The baths are separate anyway. \NYou can go on without me, Manager.}Phòng tắm riêng nên anh cứ đi trước đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.12,0:17:49.05,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{I'll wait. You can take your time.}Tôi sẽ chờ em, cứ từ từ mà tìm.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.05,0:17:51.13,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}{You can't take your time!}Đừng có từ từ chứ!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.21,0:17:54.46,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Crap...}Chết...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.46,0:17:55.98,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{Did you say something?}Anh mới nói gì hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.98,0:17:57.07,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{Not me.}Không.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.07,0:17:58.99,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{I thought I heard a voice.}Em có nghe giọng ai mà...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.99,0:18:00.22,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{Was it from outside?}Từ bên ngoài à?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.22,0:18:02.60,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{I think it was from in the closet...}Em nghĩ trong tủ...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.60,0:18:05.34,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Oh, no, no, no!}Chết chết chết!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.94,0:18:16.06,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{It's your special Senpai heating pad!}Sưởi ấm kiểu đàn chị nè!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.06,0:18:17.45,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{S-Senpai?!}C-Chị ơi?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.45,0:18:19.74,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Is it warm?}Có ấm không?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.74,0:18:21.57,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Yes, incredibly...}Có... và sướng lắm...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.57,0:18:23.80,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Wait, heating pad?!}Khoan, cái gì mà sưởi ấm?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.80,0:18:26.04,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{That's right. Sneezing and sweating...}Phải. Hắt xì và ra mồ hôi...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.04,0:18:28.08,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{You definitely need warming up.}Em cần phải được làm ấm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.14,0:18:31.58,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{It really is coming from in there...}Quả nhiên là trong tủ...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.32,0:18:33.63,Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Oh, no!}Chết!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.09,0:18:36.24,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Senpai heating pad!}Để chị sưởi ấm cho.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.24,0:18:40.57,Main,Shinozkai,0,0,0,,{W-W-Wait, now's not the time! Please, let go!}Khoan đã! Không phải lúc này! Mau thả em ra!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.57,0:18:43.35,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{It's an adhesive, and not going anywhere!}Em càng nói thế chị càng không thả.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.52,0:18:47.32,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Feeling warm?}Thấy ấm áp chưa?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.52,0:18:48.10,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Crap, crap, crap!}Nguy quá! Nguy quá!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.10,0:18:54.52,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Senpai... please, quiet down for a sec.}Chị làm ơn im lặng một chút!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.87,0:18:59.37,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{Maybe you're imagining it.}Em tưởng tượng ra à?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.37,0:19:00.61,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{I guess.}Có khi thế.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.16,0:19:04.43,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}{We're saved...}May quá...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.43,0:19:06.45,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Shinozaki-san...}Shinozaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.96,0:19:07.98,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Your hand...}Tay em...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.86,0:19:10.33,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Your hand's on my chest.}Tay em đang bóp vếu chị...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.24,0:19:16.68,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{Did you hear that?}Anh có nghe không?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.68,0:19:17.77,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{Yeah...}Ừm...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.51,0:19:21.13,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{Come to think of it, \Na long time ago, this inn was where—}Nghĩ lại thì cái nhà trọ này ngày xưa--
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.13,0:19:22.39,Main,Hayakwa,0,0,0,,{Stop it right now!}Dừng lại đi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.48,0:19:26.30,Main,Hayakwa,0,0,0,,{We were enjoying this trip together...}Chúng ta đang tận hưởng chuyến du lịch...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.88,0:19:32.25,Main,Hayakwa,0,0,0,,{Wait, is the reason \Nthey're missing because of ghosts?!}Không lẽ họ bị ma bắt đi rồi...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.16,0:19:34.90,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{We can't rule that out.}Không thể phủ nhận.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.90,0:19:38.04,Main,Hayakwa,0,0,0,,{Wh-Wh-What do we do?! \NCall the police?! An exorcist?!}P-P-phải làm sao đây? Gọi cảnh sát? Thầy trừ tà?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.04,0:19:40.31,Main,Hayakwa,0,0,0,,Mau đi tìm họ thôi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.22,0:19:40.87,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{Hayakawa-san, calm down!}Hayakawa, bình tĩnh.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.34,0:19:45.99,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{That voice... Hayakawa-shan?}Giọng đó... Hayakawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.12,0:19:50.04,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Hayakawa-shan! I'm right here!}Hayakawa, chị ở đây nè!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.35,0:19:52.50,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Senpai's going out!}Chị ấy đang bò ra!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.50,0:19:54.81,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}{What do I do, what do I do?!}Phải làm gì đây?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.76,0:20:00.76,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Hayakawa... san...}Hayakawa...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.44,0:20:06.76,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{H-Huh? It's all dark...}Ủa? Sao tối thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.76,0:20:08.17,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{Help!}Cứu!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.85,0:20:12.16,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{Hayakawa-san! Wait up!}Hayakawa! Khoan đã!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.16,0:20:14.79,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{We managed to avoid being found...}Phù, tí thì bị phát hiện.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.41,0:20:18.58,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}{She's asleep.}Chị ấy ngủ rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.99,0:20:23.66,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I guess that wraps this up... I hope.}Giờ thì... có vẻ yên tĩnh lại rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.12,0:20:26.36,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Shinozaki-san...}Shinozaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.36,0:20:28.91,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Are you okay?}Em ổn chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.97,0:20:33.77,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Senpai, you're gonna catch a cold like that.}Chị sẽ bị cảm nếu nằm ở đây đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.77,0:20:35.42,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Let's get you in a futon.}Lên futon ngủ thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.42,0:20:37.02,Main,Shhiori,0,0,0,,{'Kay...}Ừm...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.27,0:20:43.68,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}{She was worried about \Nhow she came across before...}Chị ấy đã lo lắng nhiều chuyện...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.96,0:20:48.10,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}{But I'm glad I got to see \Na different side of you, Senpai.}Nhưng thật vui khi được thấy \Nnhiều mặt khác của chị ấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.87,0:20:53.81,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Her hands...}Tay...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.01,0:20:59.80,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}{She won't let go...}Không thả ra...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.80,0:21:02.82,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Oh, this is really bad!}Tệ quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.02,0:21:05.05,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{Right this way!}Lối này!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.05,0:21:06.82,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{There's a ghost in this room!}Có ma trong phòng!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.27,0:21:18.25,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{Hello, Onee-san? \NPrepare some red beans and rice.}Chị đấy à? Chuẩn bị xôi đậu đỏ thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.25,0:21:19.71,Main,Yutaka,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I see. A wedding it is.}Ồ, cưới rồi à?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.71,0:21:21.32,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Stop!}Dừng lại!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.88,0:21:23.39,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{\an8}{Oh, what a glorious day!}Một ngày trọng đại!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.32,0:21:23.15,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Uh, look, this is actually—}Không, chuyện này--
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.15,0:21:25.39,Main,Hayakwa,0,0,0,,{Where's the ghost? Where'd it go?}Ma đâu? Nó đâu rồi?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.39,0:21:26.99,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\an8}{Senpai, could you wake up \Nand help me explain? Please...}Chị có thể dậy và giải thích hộ em được không?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.32,0:21:26.17,Main,Yutaka,0,0,0,,{I better look into venues...}Để tôi mang lễ đường đến...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.37,0:21:27.97,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{Wait, what was going on?}Khoan đã, chuyện này là sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.99,0:21:29.90,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{\an8}{Oh, I actually know someone \Nwho can help with that.}Không sao, tôi có sẵn rồi. 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.97,0:21:30.26,Main,Yutaka,0,0,0,,{And I'll be aiding \Nwith dress selection, of course.}Vậy tôi sẽ chọn váy cưới cho cô dâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.90,0:21:31.74,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{\an8}{So much fun...}Vui quá...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.26,0:21:32.97,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{You've got it all wrong!}Mọi người hiểu lầm rồi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.30,0:21:50.18,Italics,Lyrics,0,0,0,,{\an8}{Bleary-eyed and not fully awake from a dream}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.18,0:21:55.08,Italics,Lyrics,0,0,0,,{\an8}{I still can't bring myself \Nto drink that bitter coffee}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.64,0:21:59.56,Italics,Lyrics,0,0,0,,{\an8}{So I sneakily toss in \Ntwo pinches of a sweet secret}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.56,0:22:03.78,Italics,Lyrics,0,0,0,,{\an8}{And let it slowly spread throughout}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.00,0:22:08.74,Italics,Lyrics,0,0,0,,{\an8}{There's a local bakery \Nthat's only open sometimes}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.74,0:22:13.63,Italics,Lyrics,0,0,0,,{\an8}{Where I once had some toast that glittered}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.29,0:22:18.13,Italics,Lyrics,0,0,0,,{\an8}{What is it that makes it so satisfying?}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.13,0:22:22.30,Italics,Lyrics,0,0,0,,{\an8}{Almost like magic}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.72,0:22:27.38,Italics,Lyrics,0,0,0,,{\an8}{I find myself thinking about that kind of thing}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.38,0:22:32.99,Italics,Lyrics,0,0,0,,{\an8}{How the small things can be the most precious}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.74,0:22:37.78,Italics,Lyrics,0,0,0,,{\an8}{Deep inside my heart}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.78,0:22:42.18,Italics,Lyrics,0,0,0,,{\an8}{It's ever so bittersweet}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.05,0:22:47.10,Italics,Lyrics,0,0,0,,{\an8}{"Just being around you is enough"}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.10,0:22:51.12,Italics,Lyrics,0,0,0,,{\an8}{Becomes my mantra}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.12,0:22:53.41,Italics,Lyrics,0,0,0,,{\an8}{Baby like sugar}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.52,0:23:02.74,Italics,Lyrics,0,0,0,,{\an8}{Baby you're the sugar}
